Race.SpecificTitle: Gravity Drainage District No. 2 -- 3 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Gravity Drainage District No. 2 Proposition
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Gravity Drainage District No. 2 of Tensas Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of three (3) mills on all property subject to taxation within the District (an estimated $77,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2022 and ending with the year 2031, for the purpose of maintaining and improving the gravity drainage works of the District?
